title: Farewell Friends
description: Pato is leaving: he's packed his bags, he's said goodbye to his room and all his things. He's had one last sniff of his favorite flowers and said goodbye to Caterpillar, Alien, Baby Bird and Sleepy Bird. And there's the plane he's leaving inâ€¦! One last chance to say good bye. Good bye Pato!!! Everyone is waving and saying goodbye. Pato gets in the plane. One last wave. It's so sad!!! The plane goes in a circle one super-quick time and then Pato's home again. Hooray. Time for a welcome home party - and for someone else to have a go!
